metadata.description:
Cryptonauts are a deflationary set of interstellar NFTs that give holders exclusive access to a galaxy of DeFi and NFT drops.

Created by Blockzero Labs, this Cryptonaut is a unique 1 of 1 design and part of 10 Tier One NFTs.

Each Cryptonaut comes preloaded with XIO governance tokens that enable holders the ability to vote on which future projects to build and launch.

At any point in time, each Cryptonaut owner can sacrifice their NFT by burning it to redeem its underlying tokens.
metadata.name: Cryptonaut #001
